The biggest move of the day,
Bolt Enterprises.

01:18.745 --> 01:21.899
The stock is up $6.82,
sparked by reports

01:21.999 --> 01:25.152
that Goddard Bolt intends
to purchase a prime section

01:25.252 --> 01:27.755
of Downtown Los Angeles real estate.

01:31.883 --> 01:33.744
'Morning, Mr. Bolt.

01:33.844 --> 01:35.346
'Morning.

01:37.264 --> 01:38.415
- 'Morning.
- 'Morning.

